  "title": "Western Cook (Singaporean / PR) – Sloppy Shack, Downtown East",
  "description": "<h3>About Us</h3><p>Sloppy Shack , located at Downtown East, Pasir Ris, is a Halal-certified F&B brand known for hearty Western comfort food served with a local twist. We pride ourselves on creating a welcoming dining experience for families, friends, and food lovers across Singapore.</p><h3>Role & Responsibilities</h3><p>We are looking for a dedicated <strong>Western Cook</strong> to join our kitchen team. You will play a key role in delivering consistent, high-quality dishes that reflect our brand’s standards.</p><ul><li><p>Prepare and cook Western cuisine (burgers, pastas, grills, etc.) according to recipes and quality standards.</p></li><li><p>Ensure food safety and hygiene practices are strictly followed in line with <strong>SFA</strong> and <strong>MOM</strong> requirements.</p></li><li><p>Assist in daily kitchen operations including inventory management, food preparation, and cleaning.</p></li><li><p>Work closely with the Head Chef and team to maintain smooth service flow.</p></li><li><p>Contribute ideas for menu development and seasonal specials.</p></li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Singapore Citizen or Permanent Resident (PR) only.</p></li><li><p>Prior experience in Western cuisine preferred (minimum 2 years).</p></li><li><p>Strong knowledge of kitchen operations and food safety standards.</p></li><li><p>Ability to work in a fast-paced environment with a positive attitude.</p></li><li><p>Team player with good communication skills.</p></li></ul><h3>What We Offer</h3><ul><li><p>Competitive salary package ($3,500 – $3,800 onwards).</p></li><li><p>Opportunities for career growth within our expanding F&B group.</p></li><li><p>Staff meals and uniform provided.</p></li><li><p>Supportive and multicultural team environment.<br /></p><p><strong>Interested Applicants, please Whatsapp: 91370491 (Mr Sulaiman)</strong></p></li></ul>",
